{"tid":2094384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日媒：北京為貫徹港區國安法擬派約300武警駐港","createTime":"2020-07-04T14:58:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T14:58:58.000Z","uid":275104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8ef268290a1e273d38c1f1d6ab54aa8644014988","tid":2094384,"uid":275104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:58:58.000Z","msg":"日本共同社引述消息說，北京為貫徹港區國安法，將派遣200至300名武警以觀察員身份駐港。<br />\n<br />\n港區國安法，明確規定分裂國家、顛覆國家政權、恐怖活動、勾結外國或者境外勢力危害國家安全等4類罪行和相應處罰，在內地，武警其中一項主要職責是擔負反恐任務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1329030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1329030&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmpktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=0133dec0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1329030</a>"}]}